# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Career OS — environment variables
# Copy to ".env.local" for local dev, or set these in Vercel.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Cloud sync (cross-device). Set automatically when you connect a
# Vercel KV / Upstash Redis database to the project. You normally
# do NOT type these by hand — Vercel injects them.
# KV_REST_API_URL=
# KV_REST_API_TOKEN=

# Optional password to protect your deployment. If set, anyone opening
# the app must enter this key once. Leave unset for no password.
# ACCESS_PASSWORD=moja-tajna-sifra
